OL,3,CElectricity prices to be reduced by 5%
OL,4,Cfrom April in the Isle of Man
OL,6,FThe cost of electricity in the Isle of
OL,7,FMan is set to drop by 5.1% in April.
OL,9,FManx Utilities had originally
OL,10,Fannounced plans for a 5.7% increase,
OL,11,Fbut a change in the price of wholesale
OL,12,Fgas has influenced that decision.
OL,14,FIslanders will see an average
OL,15,Freduction of approximately #50 a year.
OL,17,FHowever, electricity standing charges,
OL,18,Fwater and waste water charges will
OL,19,Fstill increase by 5.7%, as previously
OL,20,Fannounced.
